name: warung makan babi guling pak kecap
address: jalan raya tanah asri sibang gede, Darmasaba, Kec. Abiansemal, Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80352, Indonesia
review 1:
Recently we tried several Babi Guling restaurants all in one day so that we could compare them.
I  am very pleased to say that this place came out as our favourite place
It's easy to find.
There's plenty of parking space at the front of the shop.
The staff were very helpful and friendly with big smiles.
The restaurant is very clean
The food is tasty and well presented.
The portion sizes are quite large.
The food was tasty (the best taste of the day)
The prices are local and very reasonable (this got me thinking that some other places maybe overcharge)
They are open 24 hours..how awesome is that!!
So....
Would I come back again?
Most Definitely!!!

name: Umahkade.Riverside
address: Unnamed Road, C686+W9C, Sibang Gede, Kec. Abiansemal, Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80352, Indonesia
review 1: Beautiful apartment in the middle of Bali. You have access to anywhere in Bali. Great host, willing to help with anything. I definitely recommend this place, it‚Äôs clean, spacious, and safe. Beautiful river flowing in the back, great working air conditioner, and wi-fi. Has all you need for a perfect stay
review 2: Amazing apartment for a great price. It's right in the middle of bali and you can easily go anywhere from this central location. Its local people with local prices... away from all the touristy places with all those high prices. The best thing about the apartment was the sound of the flowing water just behind the place... seen from the balcony. Would recommend it to anyone... it's got all ur basic needs... great for long stays. Good internet connection. No power outages, close to shops and some good street food. Very safe area. Hosts are amazing people and will help you with anything, very good people. A must stay if you are coming to bali to see it all. They have motorbike rental for a great price.... good to get you to all those great places to see in bali.
review 3: I love this apartment very relaxing and you always have a good vibes with nature since it in a riverside, we've been here for like almost 2months, the host is very hospitable, kind and thoughtful. We enjoyed our stay so much
review 4: a good place when you want to relax in the rain with a cup of tea
review 5: Great apartment with reasonable price, great view from terrace, great host who is open to help on anything. great place who is looking for place in the center of Bali
